caption%3EThe%20pool%20at%20Kibale%20Lodge.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20short%20walk%20from%20my%20room%20was%20Kibale's%20spa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20massage%20rooms%2C%20a%20swimming%20pool%20overlooking%20the%20jungle%2C%20and%20a%20sauna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuests%20at%20Kibale%20can%20receive%20complimentary%20massages%2C%20and%20spending%20an%20afternoon%20at%20the%20pool%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20pass%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Kibale%20is%20a%20main%20lodge%2C%20where%20meals%20are%20served%20and%20cocktails%20are%20sipped.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20entrance%20to%20the%20main%20lodge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb431a466d2b74ab33cc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20the%20main%20lodge.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20my%20room%2C%20elements%20across%20the%20main%20lodge%20came%20from%20the%20surrounding%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interior%20was%20filled%20with%20warm%20woods%2C%20natural%20walls%2C%20and%20rattan%20furniture.%20A%20dining%20table%20stretched%20across%20one%20area%20of%20the%20room%2C%20where%20guests%20were%20encouraged%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20communal%20dinner%20each%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20menu%20changed%20each%20night%20I%20was%20there%2C%20but%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20locally%20inspired%20foods.%20I%20had%20catfish%20one%20evening%20and%20butternut%20squash%20another.%20For%20breakfast%2C%20I%20tried%20traditional%20Ugandan%20katogo%2C%20a%20dish%20typically%20made%20with%20green%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFrom%20the%20lodge%2C%20guests%20can%20adventure%20on%20hiking%20trails%20that%20lead%20to%20lookout%20points%20and%20crater%20lakes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20from%20the%20lodge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb461c6ad288d147e39de%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20from%20the%20lodge.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20different%20hiking%20paths%20start%20from%20Kibale%20Lodge.%20Guests%20can%20walk%20up%20to%20a%20viewpoint%20during%20sunset%20or%20take%20a%20longer%20hike%20around%20a%20nearby%20crater%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20afternoon%20at%20Kibale%20was%20spent%20on%20a%20guided%20hike%20with%20Kibale%20staff%20member%20Saidi%2C%20who%20pointed%20out%20different%20species%20of%20birds%20and%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20lodge's%20main%20appeal%20is%20its%20proximity%20to%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chimpanzee%20in%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb48ac6ad288d147e39ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chimpanzee%20in%20the%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKibale%20National%20Park%20sits%2030%20minutes%20away%20from%20the%20lodge.%20The%20forest%20is%20home%20to%2013%20species%20of%20primates%2C%20making%20it%20the%20primate%20capital%20of%20the%20world.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20park%20has%20more%20than%201%2C500%20chimpanzees.%20So%2C%20while%20travelers%20can%20view%20species%20like%20the%20red%20colobus%2C%20black-and-white%20colobus%2C%20and%20L'Hoest's%20monkeys%20in%20the%20park%2C%20many%20arrive%20for%20chimpanzee%20trekking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20morning%20at%20Kibale%2C%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolcanoes%20Safaris%20coordinated%20my%20chimpanzee%20trekking%20plans%20and%20secured%20my%20permit%2C%20which%20costs%20%24250%20and%20is%20included%20in%20the%20price%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvolcanoessafaris.com%2Fsafari%2F7-day-chimpanzee-safari%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoutfitter's%20safari%20packages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKiwanuka%20drove%20me%2030%20minutes%20to%20the%20forest%2C%20where%20I%20met%20a%20ranger%20with%20the%20Uganda%20Wildlife%20Authority.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20ranger%20tracks%20in%20chimpanzee%20in%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb667c6ad288d147e3a81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter's%20ranger%20tracks%20chimpanzees%20in%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20woke%20up%20in%20Kibale%20Lodge%20to%20the%20chirps%20of%20birds%20like%20Ross's%20turaco%2C%20then%20came%20the%20roosters%20and%20noises%20from%20the%20nearby%20village%20coming%20alive.%20The%20final%20sound%20was%20from%20my%20butler%2C%20who%20reminded%20me%20that%20I%20had%20a%20chimpanzee%20trek%20in%20just%20a%20few%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breakfast%2C%20Kiwanuka%20drove%20me%20and%20another%20traveler%20to%20Kibale%20National%20Park.%20As%20we%20made%20our%20way%20through%20the%20forest%2C%20we%20searched%20the%20canopies%20for%20red%20and%20black-and-white%20colobus%20monkeys.%20We%20stopped%20on%20the%20road%20while%20waiting%20for%20a%20troop%20of%20baboons%20to%20cross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20trailhead%20for%20chimpanzee%20trekking.%20Here%2C%20I%20met%20Bosco%20Bwambale%2C%20our%20ranger%20with%20the%20Uganda%20Wildlife%20Authority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20with%20three%20other%20trackers%2C%20and%20before%20heading%20deeper%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20Bwambale%20gave%20a%20briefing%20on%20what%20to%20expect%20during%20the%20chimp%20trek.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20would%20hike%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20where%20another%20set%20of%20trackers%20had%20sights%20on%20the%20Kanyantale%20chimp%20community.%20Once%20we%20found%20the%20chimpanzees%2C%20we%20would%20put%20on%20face%20masks%20and%20observe%20them%20for%20an%20hour.%20Then%2C%20we%20would%20hike%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20headed%20into%20the%20dense%20forest%2C%20where%20we%20followed%20elephant%20tracks%20and%20listened%20to%20radio%20calls%20from%20the%20trackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBwambale%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20ranger%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades%2C%20saw%20the%20chimpanzees%20long%20before%20I%20did.%20They%20were%20in%20the%20branches%20above%20us%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20moments%2C%20they%20let%20out%20screams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBwambale%20explained%20that%20the%20shrieks%20were%20notifying%20others%20that%20they%20had%20found%20food%2C%20and%20that%20it%20was%20lunchtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20got%20closer%2C%20I%20saw%20them%20on%20the%20move%20%E2%80%94%20jumping%20from%20branch%20to%20branch%2C%20sliding%20down%20thick%20vines%2C%20and%20moving%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20they%20settled%20down%20in%20one%20area%2C%20where%20I%20watched%20them%20groom%20one%20another%2C%20eat%2C%20and%20explore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20hours%20of%20my%20life%2C%20and%20I%20left%20dreaming%20of%20a%20return%20trip%20to%20Kibale%20Lodge.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chimpanzee%20in%20a%20tree.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb6543fe8d39283632480%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chimpanzee%20in%20a%20tree.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20eyed%20the%20ears%20and%20hands%20that%20felt%20reminiscent%20of%20my%20own.%20I%20watched%20the%2030-or-so%20chimpanzees%20interact%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20I%20was%20there%20long%20enough%20to%20see%20a%20bit%20of%20each%20primate's%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERangers%20like%20Bwambale%20have%20given%20each%20chimp%20a%20name%2C%20and%20Bwambale%20shared%20tidbits%20about%20their%20lives%2C%20like%20Budha%2C%20who%20is%20calm%20and%20known%20for%20stretching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hiking%20back%20out%2C%20we%20drove%20back%20to%20Kibale%20Lodge%2C%20where%20I%20spent%20the%20afternoon%20sipping%20coffee%20and%20reflecting%20on%20the%20experience%2C%20eager%20to%20start%20planning%20a%20return%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkibale-lodge-uganda-review-chimpanzee-trekking%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745314081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb942a466d2b74ab33e0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkibale-lodge-uganda-review-chimpanzee-trekking%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20stayed%20at%20Kibale%20Lodge%20in%20Uganda.%20The%20luxury%20property%20is%20a%2030-minute%20drive%20from%20Kibale%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20primate%20capital%20of%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mhumphries%40businessinsider.com%20(Monica%20Humphries)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkibale-lodge-uganda-review-chimpanzee-trekking%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Benedict%20IX%3A%20The%20Youngest%20Pope%20In%20History%20And%20The%20Turmoil%20That%20Followed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Catholic%20Church%20is%20in%20mourning%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Pope%20Francis.%20As%20is%20customary%2C%20with%20the%20death%20of%20a%20pope%2C%20the%20process%20of%20selecting%20a%20new%20leader%20for%20the%20Church%20is%20already%20underway.%22%2C%22p