0has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20graduated%20in%201999%20with%20an%20accounting%20and%20finance%20degree%20and%20started%20my%20career%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-become-big-four-partner-pwc-ey-deloitte-kpmg-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKPMG%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20auditor.%20I%20quickly%20realized%20it%20wasn't%20the%20right%20energy%20and%20environment%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20I%20made%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20and%20moved%20from%20Chicago%20to%20Los%20Angeles%20without%20an%20apartment.%20I%20had%20only%20ever%20spent%20two%20days%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20got%20there%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoming-out-gay-then-came-out-nonbinary-lgbtq-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20came%20out%20as%20gay%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20got%20a%20senior%20financial%20analyst%20job%20for%20a%20production%20company%20on%20the%20Fox%20studio%20lot.%20Through%20my%20network%20and%20relationship%20with%20the%20founder%20I%20met%20in%20LA%2C%20I%20became%20employee%2010%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadtech-companies-that-are-trying-to-preserve-ad-targeting-and-measurement-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGumGum%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20adtech%20firm%2C%20as%20the%20VP%20of%20finance%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20this%20involved%20moving%20boxes%20into%20a%20U-Haul.%20I%20grew%20with%20the%20company%20and%20was%20appointed%20CEO%20six%20years%20ago.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20about%20500%20employees%20in%2020%20countries%20and%20are%20valued%20at%20nearly%20%24700%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20my%20career%2C%20I've%20had%20regrets%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20mistakes%20I've%20learned%20from.%20These%20are%20the%20four%20biggest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a21e248b-3283-47cd-8ea8-9e07be235965%5C%22%3E%3Cst