%20to%20more%20urgent%20projects%2C%20the%20documents%20explained.%20The%20system%20also%20offers%20a%20simplified%20networking%20setup%20and%20security%20updates%2C%20while%20alerting%20employees%20and%20leaders%20to%20projects%20with%20low%20GPU%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Amazon%20employees%20are%20%26quot%3Bmandated%26quot%3B%20to%20go%20through%20Greenland%20to%20obtain%20GPU%20capacity%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20future%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20company%20expects%20this%20to%20increase%20efficiency%20by%20%26quot%3Breducing%20idle%20capacity%20and%20optimizing%20cluster%20utilization%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22682b2dcf-247b-4468-9f6b-109f452c441a%5C%22%3E%241%20billion%20investment%20in%20AI-related%20projects%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20retail%20business%20is%20wasting%20no%20time%20putting%20its%20GPUs%20to%20work.%20One%20document%20listed%20more%20than%20160%20AI-powered%20initiatives%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-predicts-700-million-potential-gain-ai-assistant-rufus-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERufus%3C%2Fa%3E%20shopping%20assistant%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-theia-amazon-ai-tool-shopping-inspiration-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETheia%3C%2Fa%3E%20product%20image%20generator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20AI%20projects%20in%20the%20works%20include%2C%20per%20the%20document%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20vision-assisted%20package%20retrieval%20(VAPR)%20service%20that%20uses%20computer-vision%20technology%20to%20help%20drivers%20quickly%20identify%20and%20pick%20the%20correct%20packages%20from%20vans%20at%20delivery%20stops.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20service%20that%20automatically%20pulls%20in%20data%20from%20external%20websites%20to%20create%20consistent%20product%20information.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20AI%20model%20that%20optimizes%20driver%20routing%20and%20package