that%20scope%20came%20massive%20risk.%20Building%20and%20scaling%20cell%20manufacturing%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20outside%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20is%20notoriously%20difficult.%20Northvolt%20struggled%20to%20ramp%20up%20operations%20at%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorthvolt-trying-fix-electric-vehicle-supply-chain-battery-recycling-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArctic%20Circle%20facility%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20increasingly%20relied%20on%20Chinese%20equipment%2C%20which%20slowed%20production%20and%20created%20bottlenecks.%20Costs%20ballooned%2C%20debts%20mounted%2C%20and%20the%20company%20ultimately%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorthvolt-european-battery-startup-cutting-jobs-sweden-ev-tesla-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecouldn't%20keep%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNorthvolt%20went%20a%20little%20too%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20investor%20who%20has%20backed%20startups%20in%20this%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThey%20tried%20to%20commercialize%20before%20perfecting%20the%20process%20at%20scale.%26quot%3B%20This%20person%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20sensitive%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENorthvolt%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230462b3f-d601-4dbf-8939-5c42991bc8d2%5C%22%3ERedwood%20wants%20to%20be%20'Switzerland'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERedwood%20Materials%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20focuses%20on%20what%20it%20sees%20as%20the%20most%20valuable%20%E2%80%94%20and%20underinvested%20%E2%80%94%20piece%20of%20the%20EV%20battery%20supply%20chain%3A%20cathode%20active%20materials.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cofounder-digs-for-the-new-black-gold-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECAM%3C%2Fa%3E%20accounts%20for%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20a%20battery's%20value%20and%2015%25%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20an%20electric%20vehicle%2C%20according%20to%20Redwood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20large-scale%20CAM%20production%20in%20North%20America%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20gap%20Redwood%20wants%20to%20fill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20making%20battery%20cells.%20That's%20never%20been%20part%20of%20the%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cal%20Lankton%2C%20Redwood's%20chief%20commercial%20officer.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20want%20to%20compete%20with%20our%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Redwood%20recycles%20EV%20battery%20production%20scrap%20and%20old%20batteries%20into%20usable%20metals%20and%20refines%20them%20into%20CAM%2C%20which%20it%20sells%20to%20cell%20manufacturers%20such%20as%20Panasonic%20and%20Toyota.%20This%20strategy%20keeps%20the%20company%20neutral%20while%20generating%20revenue%20from%20multiple%20points%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20JB%20would%20say%2C%20we%20can%20be%20Switzerland%2C%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20told%20me%20when%20I%20met%20him%20recently%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fredwood-materials-largest-us-battery-recycler-photos-huge-campus-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERedwood's%20campus%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nevada's%20high%20desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Northvolt%2C%20which%20produced%20its%20own%20batteries%20and%20used%20its%20recycled%20material%20internally%2C%20Redwood%20aims%20to%20sell%20its%20refined%20materials%20to%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20customers%2C%20reducing%20dependency%20on%20any%20one%20player%20and%20avoiding%20direct%20competition%20with%20partners%20that%20make%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Northvolt%20set%20out%20to%20build%20is%20incredibly%20impressive%20%E2%80%94%20the%20scope%2C%20the%20aspiration%20of%20what%20they%20tried%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20come%20across%20at%20all%20as%20denigrating%20what%20happened.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20that%20by%20trying%20to%20make%20batteries%20itself%2C%20Northvolt%20added%20extra%20layers%20of%20risk%2C%20complexity%2C%20and%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20competing%20with%20your%20customers.%20So%20you%20would%20only%20produce%20CAM%20for%20your%20own%20consumption%2C%20which%20was%20Northvolt's%20plan%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20if%20any%20piece%20in%20there%20falls%20apart%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20breaks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290d24f52-9c0f-45f7-8cdd-0d0ca37884e2%5C%22%3EStep-by-step%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERedwood%20has%20also%20been%20more%20measured%20in%20its%20scaling.%20While%20Northvolt%20attempted%20to%20go%20from%20lab%20to%20commercial%20production%20in%20one%20giant%20leap%2C%20Redwood%20moves%20step-by-step%20%E2%80%94%20refining%20materials%2C%20building%20CAM%20capacity%2C%20and%20only%20taking%20on%20new%20challenges%20when%20it's%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Lankton%20said%20that%20while%20Redwood%20initially%20intended%20to%20hold%20onto%20intermediate%20recycled%20materials%20until%20its%20CAM%20operations%20ramped%20up%2C%20the%20company%20made%20a%20tactical%20pivot%3A%20sell%20the%20intermediate%20products%20now%2C%20generate%20revenue%2C%20and%20prove%20its%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20dollar%20today%20for%20a%20company%20in%20our%20position%20is%20much%20more%20valuable%20than%20a%20dollar%20to%20use%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20convert%20that%20inventory%20into%20cash.%20Let's%20demonstrate%20our%20capability%20to%20our%20investors%2C%20to%20our%20customers%2C%20to%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedwood%20also%20used%20to%20make%20copper%20foil%2C%20a%20main%20ingredient%20in%20batteries.%20When%20Chinese%20companies%20began%20churning%20this%20out%20in%20massive%20quantities%2C%20prices%20plummeted%2C%20so%20Redwood%20halted%20that%20part%20of%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20dogmatic%2C%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20take%20a%20business%20plan%20and%20just%20do%20it%20until%20we%20think%20it%20works%20and%20run%20ourselves%20into%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201e89b60-b28a-4015-9345-ae8ce8500985%5C%22%3ELessons%20from%20Northvolt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENorthvolt's%20bankruptcy%20isn't%20just%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20live%20case%20study.%20The%20company's%20downfall%20underscores%20the%20perils%20of%20over-integration%2C%20overreach%2C%20and%20underestimating%20the%20difficulty%20of%20battery%20cell%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERedwood%20Materials%20is%20learning%20and%20taking%20a%20different%20tack%20by%20positioning%20itself%20not%20as%20a%20battery%20maker%2C%20but%20as%20an%20enabler%20of%20the%20EV%20battery%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20strengths%20of%20Redwood%2C%20and%20I%20again%2C%20not%20to%20put%20too%20fine%20a%20point%20on%20it%2C%20something%20that%20Northvolt%20kind%20of%20struggled%20with%2C%20which%20is%20finding%20those%20pivot%20points%20when%20the%20original%20plan%20perhaps%20is%20getting%20more%20expensive%20or%20further%20out%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Lankton%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorthvolt-bankruptcy-redwood-materials-ev-batteries-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745312402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680040653fe8d39283634aad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorthvolt-bankruptcy-redwood-materials-ev-batteries-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Northvolt's%20%2415%20billion%20collapse%20shook%20the%20cleantech%20industry.%20Rival%20Redwood%20Materials%20takes%20a%20different%20approach%20in%20several%20key%20ways.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40bu