%20Images%3B%20Chelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Tesla%20launched%20the%20Cybertruck%20in%202023%2C%20it%20was%20the%20product%20of%20four%20years%20of%20hype.%20The%20boxy%20electric%20pickup%20was%20the%20company's%20first%20new%20model%20since%202020.%20Kim%20Kardashian%2C%20Pharrell%20Williams%2C%20and%20Justin%20Bieber%20were%20spotted%20riding%20around%20in%20it.%20With%20a%20million%20people%20on%20the%20truck's%20reservation%20list%20and%20a%20%24120%2C000%20price%20tag%2C%20it%20quickly%20became%20a%20status%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20years%20later%2C%20the%20waitlist%20has%20disappeared.%20Trucks%20are%20piling%20up%20in%20sales%20lots.%20Fewer%20than%2050%2C000%20vehicles%20have%20been%20delivered.%20Some%20owners%20have%20become%20political%20targets%20thanks%20to%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk's%20association%20with%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20a%20quiet%20rebrand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20Tesla%20has%20moved%20to%20position%20the%20Cybertruck%20as%20a%20working%20man's%20vehicle%20%E2%80%94%20less%20DeLorean%2C%20more%20Ford%20F-150.%20The%20company%20updated%20its%20website%2C%20ditching%20an%20other-worldly%20aesthetic%20for%20images%20that%20feature%20the%20truck%20hauling%20equipment%20and%20an%20Airstream%20trailer.%20And%20sales%20workers%20at%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it's%20become%20increasingly%20difficult%20to%20move%20the%20truck%20off%20sales%20lots.%20The%20vehicle%2C%20they%20said%2C%20needs%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20traditional%20truck%20buyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPitching%20it%20to%20truck%20people%20is%20more%20about%20the%20functionality%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20salesperson%20who%20works%20in%20the%20South.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20know%20how%20much%20it%20can%20tow%2C%20how%20much%20can%20fit%20in%20the%20truck%20bed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20company%20prepares%20to%20deliver%20first%20quarter%20earnings%2C%20it%20faces%20sluggish%20delivery%20numbers%2C%20a%20brand%20crisis%2C%20and%20a%20stock%20price%20down%20over%2043%25%20year%20to%20date%20%E2%80%94%20and%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20boost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20initially%20pushed%20too%20hard%20into%20the%20out-of-this-world%20aesthetic%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivan%20Drury%2C%20the%20director%20of%20insight%20for%20the%20automotive%20research%20firm%20Edmunds%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20only%20appeals%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20market.%20Now%20they%20need%20to%20take%20a%20more%20traditional%20route.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a01a33d-9f0f-4f28-8d67-37ace033fabb%5C%22%3ETaking%20on%20the%20traditional%20truck%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20recently%20as%20April%209%2C%20Tesla's%20website%20included%20renderings%20of%20the%20truck%20in%20a%20Mars-like%20atmosphere%20and%20ad%20copy%20that%20touted%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bbuilt%20for%20any%20planet%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bcabin%20as%20quiet%20as%20outer%20space.%26quot%3B%20(The%20brand%20famously%20shies%20away%20from%20traditional%20advertising%20and%20relies%20on%20Musk%2C%20the%20website%2C%20its%20reputation%2C%20and%20its%20X%20presence%20to%20sell%20vehicles.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20Ford%20CEO%20Jim%20Farley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fford-ceo-disses-tesla-cybertruck-for-silicon-valley-people-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edismissed%20the%20Cybertruck%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20only%20for%20%26quot%3BSilicon%20Valley%20people%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blike%20a%20cool%20high-end%20product%20parked%20in%20front%20of%20a%20hotel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20make%20trucks%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Farley%20said%20shortly%20before%20the%20Cybertruck's%20release.%20%26quot%3BI%20make%20trucks%20for%20real%20people%20who%20do%20real%20work%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20truck.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-April%2C%20Tesla%20redesigned%20its%20product%20page%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20truck's%20release.%20Gone%20are%20the%20futuristic%20aesthetics%20and%20allusions%20to%20Mars%3B%20now%20the%20vehicle%20is%20fit%20for%20a%20construction%20worker%20or%20a%20family%20outing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20strikingly%20similar%20to%20advertisements%20for%20the%202024%20model%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ford.com%2Ftrucks%2Ff150%2F2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFord's%20F-150%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20best-selling%20pickup%20in%20the%20US%20for%20the%20past%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla's%20new%20Cybertruck%20page%20looks%20similar%20to%20some%20F-150%20advertisements%20from%20last%20year.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6806d96fa466d2b74ab3c063%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla's%20new%20Cybertruck%20page%20looks%20similar%20to%20some%20F-150%20advertisements.%3Cp%3ETesla%20and%20Ford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20image%20for%20both%20truck's%20webpages%20featured%20Airstream%20trailers%2C%20and%20both%20included%20images%20of%20truck%20beds%20filled%20with%20wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20and%20Ford%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Fcar-news%2Ftesla-introduces-cheaper-rwd-cybertruck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeaper%2C%20scaled-down%20version%20of%20the%20Tesla%20truck%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20launched%20in%20April%2C%20is%20also%20similar%20in%20price%2C%20range%2C%20and%20towing%20capacity%20to%20Ford's%20electric%20F-150.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Tesla%20sales%20workers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they've%20seen%20a%20push%20to%20market%20the%20vehicle%20more%20toward%20the%20typical%20truck%20buyer%20since%20late%20last%20year.%20The%20sales%20worker%20who%20works%20in%20a%20Southern%20state%20said%20the%20truck's%20flashy%20exterior%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20people%20willing%20to%20buy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20test%20drivers%20aren't%20real%20truck%20buyers%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20more%20of%20a%20novelty%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cybertruck's%20updated%20website%20focuses%20on%20the%20truck's%20functionality.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6806d9a93fe8d3928363a7f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cybertruck's%20updated%20website%20focuses%20on%20the%20truck's%20functionality.%3Cp%3EFord%20and%20Tesla%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20truck's%20%26quot%3Bbulletproof%26quot%3B%20exterior%2C%20Tesla%20struggled%20to%20market%20it%20as%20worksite-friendly%20and%20durable%20early%20on.%20Within%20weeks%20of%20its%20release%2C%20owners%20and%20critics%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20post%20Cybertruck%20fails%2C%20including%20footage%20of%20the%20truck%20getting%20stuck%20in%20snow%20or%20struggling%20to%20drive%20up%20a%20dirt%20hill.%20The%20phenomenon%20even%20spawned%20a%20popular%20Reddit%20channel%20with%20more%20than%20300%2C000%20members%20called%20%26quot%3BCyberstuck.%26quot%3B%20The%20pickup%20has%20also%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-owner-recall-trim-panel-detach-risk-hazard-2025-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTesla%2520is%2520recalling%2520just%2520over%2Cthe%2520risk%2520of%2520a%2520crash.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeight%20recalls%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20a%20typical%20truck%20owner%20may%20not%20work%20on%20a%20farm%20or%20a%20construction%20site%2C%20there's%20value%20in%20selling%20that%20image.%20Drury%20sees%20the%20new%20