ny%20hatchlings%20are%20ready%20to%20emerge.%20The%20second%20task%20is%20to%20identify%20overdue%20nests%20where%20hatchlings%20might%20be%20struggling.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20nest%20was%20due%20yesterday%20or%20the%20day%20before%20and%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20any%20activity%2C%20then%20it%20is%20time%20for%20us%20to%20excavate%20and%20take%20them%20out%20ourselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nishfa%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20hatchlings%20get%20entangled%20in%20roots%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20emerge%2C%20or%20they%20become%20dehydrated.%20Senior%20volunteers%20carefully%20excavate%20these%20nests%2C%20retrieving%20the%20remaining%20hatchlings%20while%20also%20documenting%20unhatched%2C%20sterile%2C%20or%20dead%20eggs.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20ensures%20that%20as%20many%20hatchlings%20as%20possible%20make%20it%20safely%20to%20the%20sea%2C%20giving%20them%20the%20best%20start%20in%20their%20journey%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20joy%20of%20releasing%20the%20hatchlings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20evening%20between%206%20and%207%20pm%2C%20a%20crowd%20gathers%20to%20witness%20this%20mesmerising%20event%3A%20the%20public%20hatchling%20release.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20create%20awareness%2C%20as%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20opportunity%20that%20we%20have%20to%20reach%20the%20public%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nishfa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20popularity%20of%20these%20releases%20has%20made%20crowd%20control%20a%20challenge.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20last%20year%2C%20the%20crowd%20has%20been%20quite%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nishfa%20notes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20manage%20this%2C%20volunteers%20set%20up%20bamboo%20barricades%2C%20dig%20them%20into%20the%20sand%2C%20and%20rake%20the%20area%20to%20clear%20dustbins%20and%20other%20debris%2C%20ensuring%20a%20clean%20and%20safe%20release%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO